---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Pengalaman | Haikal Luthfianino">
    <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 w-full">
        <div class="mb-12 border-b border-neutral-200 dark:border-neutral-900 pb-8">
            <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-black dark:text-white tracking-tight mb-4">Pengalaman & Project.</h1>
            <p class="text-neutral-500">Eksplorasi di ranah low-level system, hardware, dan rekayasa perangkat lunak.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
            
            <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl border border-neutral-200 dark:border-neutral-800 bg-white dark:bg-[#0a0a0a] hover:border-neutral-400 dark:hover:border-neutral-500 transition-all group shadow-sm flex flex-col justify-between">
                <div>
                    <div class="mb-4 flex justify-between items-center">
                        <span class="text-xs font-code text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400 bg-neutral-100 dark:bg-neutral-900 px-3 py-1.5 border border-neutral-200 dark:border-neutral-800 rounded-lg">Work Experience</span>
                        <span class="text-xs font-code text-neutral-500 flex items-center gap-1">
                            <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path></svg>
                            5 Bulan
                        </span>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-black dark:text-white mb-1 group-hover:underline decoration-neutral-400 dark:decoration-neutral-500 underline-offset-4">Teknisi Komputer (PKL)</h3>
                    <h4 class="text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400 font-medium mb-3">NS Komputer</h4>
                    <p class="text-neutral-500 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">
                        Menjalani Praktik Kerja Lapangan (PKL) dengan fokus pada perbaikan perangkat keras. Bertanggung jawab dalam mendiagnosis masalah komponen komputer/laptop, instalasi sistem operasi, dan memberikan solusi teknis kepada pelanggan.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl border border-neutral-200 dark:border-neutral-800 bg-white dark:bg-[#0a0a0a] hover:border-neutral-400 dark:hover:border-neutral-500 transition-all group shadow-sm flex flex-col justify-between">
                <div>
                    <div class="mb-4 flex justify-between items-center">
                        <span class="text-xs font-code text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400 bg-neutral-100 dark:bg-neutral-900 px-3 py-1.5 border border-neutral-200 dark:border-neutral-800 rounded-lg">Open Source / AOSP</span>
                        <span class="text-xs font-code text-neutral-500 flex items-center gap-1">
                            <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M8 7V3m8 4V3m-9 8h10M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z"></path></svg>
                            2023 - 2024
                        </span>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-black dark:text-white mb-1 group-hover:underline decoration-neutral-400 dark:decoration-neutral-500 underline-offset-4">Official Maintainer AfterlifeOS</h3>
                    <h4 class="text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400 font-medium mb-3">Poco F1 (beryllium)</h4>
                    <p class="text-neutral-500 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">
                        Menjadi pengelola resmi (official maintainer) sistem operasi AfterlifeOS berbasis Android. Bertanggung jawab atas kompilasi rutin (build), pengelolaan device tree, pembaruan kernel, perbaikan bug, serta memastikan stabilitas OS untuk pengguna publik.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl border border-neutral-200 dark:border-neutral-800 bg-white dark:bg-[#0a0a0a] hover:border-neutral-400 dark:hover:border-neutral-500 transition-all group shadow-sm flex flex-col justify-between">
                <div>
                    <div class="mb-4 flex justify-between items-center">
                        <span class="text-xs font-code text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400 bg-neutral-100 dark:bg-neutral-900 px-3 py-1.5 border border-neutral-200 dark:border-neutral-800 rounded-lg">Open Source / AOSP</span>
                        <span class="text-xs font-code text-neutral-500 flex items-center gap-1">
                            <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M8 7V3m8 4V3m-9 8h10M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z"></path></svg>
                            2023
                        </span>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-black dark:text-white mb-1 group-hover:underline decoration-neutral-400 dark:decoration-neutral-500 underline-offset-4">Official Maintainer BananaDroid</h3>
                    <h4 class="text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400 font-medium mb-3">Xiaomi Mi A1 (tissot)</h4>
                    <p class="text-neutral-500 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">
                        Dipercaya sebagai maintainer resmi untuk custom ROM BananaDroid. Mengelola source code, memastikan sinkronisasi repositori berjalan lancar, dan merilis build yang stabil dengan penyesuaian performa khusus untuk arsitektur perangkat.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl border border-neutral-200 dark:border-neutral-800 bg-white dark:bg-[#0a0a0a] hover:border-neutral-400 dark:hover:border-neutral-500 transition-all group shadow-sm flex flex-col justify-between">
                <div>
                    <div class="mb-4">
                        <span class="text-xs font-code text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400 bg-neutral-100 dark:bg-neutral-900 px-3 py-1.5 border border-neutral-200 dark:border-neutral-800 rounded-lg">Machine Learning</span>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-black dark:text-white mb-1 group-hover:underline decoration-neutral-400 dark:decoration-neutral-500 underline-offset-4">Hardware Diagnostics AI</h3>
                    <p class="text-neutral-500 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">
                        Pengembangan sistem pakar menggunakan algoritma K-Nearest Neighbor (KNN) untuk mengklasifikasi dan mendiagnosis kerusakan pada komponen motherboard.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </main>
</Layout>
